➜来自中国国鸟候选的质问：凭什么熊猫不是猫，我叫鸡就真是鸡了？
http://www.sohu.com/a/429898425_624188	13101
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/086018af3822488387301e62af098b95.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果被问到<strong>有什么动物能代表中国?</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家想必都有笃定的答案</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/c16073dbe67940cda5db400ce84e1142.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但如果问到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>哪种鸟类能代表中国呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201106/f0e1a25e4f7f4941896933904541b6b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">按道理来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候应该只需要一个国鸟出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能决定谁才是对的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但遗憾的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>中国并没有确定谁是国鸟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/a24ab53b838c45bca5fa3e1b25540c91.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实早年间有三位国鸟候选</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进入了最终选拔赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果却<strong>全员惨遭淘汰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这背后的原因究竟是为何</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天就让我们来回顾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《国鸟请就位》的总决赛现场——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201106/76953cbb785b4f0f88998dab5ac3aae7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/47b7c8968f074a349b1796466de650c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201106/4497e90c75be40e8b6f4c2469139fd34.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b4bff0213bb642c3b55f9342c4761a92.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>红腹锦鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭借一身绚烂夺目的羽毛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及长而飘逸的尾巴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">收获鸡界<strong>小凤凰</strong>的称号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此称号不仅闻名鸡界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更是受到不少历史学家肯定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仅凭这点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就成功拉开了与其他选手的距离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直逼<strong>国鸟C位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/89ca827f149649cda5e594e2600ab7b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭借着极高的颜值</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡受到了皇族的宠爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以性冷淡配色出圈的<strong>宋徽宗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都不禁亲自动笔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给它来了幅<strong>《芙蓉锦鸡图》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在明清文官官服的<strong>补子</strong>上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绣上红腹锦鸡的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比孔雀的品阶都高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>二品官</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201106/3dc1568c7c6248b8995cddb510194819.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除此之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡还有过一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流弊的<strong>出道经历</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>2001年世界大学生运动会</strong>开幕上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各国入场引导牌上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都用上了自家国鸟的图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然中国没国鸟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也不能直接弄个空白就上去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡临时上位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以国鸟之名出现在牌子上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼瞅着离<strong>转正</strong>也就一步之遥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201106/e8401acd1da943fcb34d596e76283959.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡最终却败下阵来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这只怪一件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">名字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201106/2587476ff102446695ecbc5fdc80b364.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡名字里的<strong>“鸡”</strong>字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让大家迟疑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟在大家传统认知里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡是鸡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸟是鸟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们选的是国鸟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你这个叫鸡的来当</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎么都感觉<strong>不太对劲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/e4e3684b6a58400ebf1e0babab94b3f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红腹锦鸡倒不是不能飞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你追鸡或者被鸡追的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">应该发现过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡是能扑腾起来的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想飞也不是大问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d5262935ea7345e1815039323c0ba351.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平时红腹锦鸡也<strong>不乐意飞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除非出现被追着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再不飞就要丢了命的情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">否则平时就搁地面散散步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样闲散的态度不可取</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是它以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没·点·鸟·样</strong>这点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与国鸟请就位奖杯失之交臂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b990611306504f58a4ba2260c53c85b0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们来看看下一位选手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d94611c5b171492c880fcebf59bf4af1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/7e24a3b8851d45e0938fceb2032e5bbb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d3dc5df94401465ea946fc7a9f59fca8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>丹顶鹤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从古代开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就长期霸占</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>中国人最爱的飞禽榜首位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑白配色低调却不失奢华</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大长腿优雅出场自带仙气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟以华丽出名的红腹锦鸡比起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤更有种水墨画般的东方气质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201106/6f6c60a911854df0acc0fea49eedf799.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而中国人为什么如此喜欢丹顶鹤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是因为它的<strong>内在品质过硬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平时为人处世都沉稳温和</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶尔跳个舞陶冶陶冶情操</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和别的动物们都能和谐相处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从来不争不抢岁月静好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b70d22a07e494e2985b9c0362b94414a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦被惹毛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">干起架来那身姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丝毫不输各类战斗界大佬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它脚踹老鹰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201106/452201d556674c7aae7db9fc958d49ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把它按地摩擦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/41acf308a25e424badfaebf736e6ef93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它单挑三虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/219e14eea077482e952b2667baaf080f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把老虎打到自闭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/8ed31dc68f96401aa25d71524d074172.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用最优雅的身姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">干着最勐的事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是真的<strong>空中勐禽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/96a40e81f78848aeb3847c6e7724f345.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了自身素质过硬外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤的背后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有<strong>顶级大佬</strong>撑腰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤寿命通常可以达到五六十年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而古人平均寿命也就三十多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以对古人来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤那是真长寿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是就经常把它和神仙组cp</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赋予它<strong>吉祥长寿</strong>的意义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201106/5a3e8f050b4a4cb0ab14f373c573629b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再加之丹顶鹤还非常专情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坚决实行<strong>一夫一妻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颜值高还专一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">优雅却还能打的人设</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讲真谁能不爱？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们对它的好感度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是蹭蹭蹭疯狂往上涨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只差一点点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就能够捧杯回家了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201106/bc70dce3b7d0420388945f5a3b92ce64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但遗憾的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤也与奖杯失之交臂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这次怪的是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201106/bd74a2d2325f47fb910f6919061b0b27.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——名字不对劲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/9561a73820d44d35b1f2c1257c5f8d3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁也没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这么中国风的丹顶鹤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的拉丁文学名居然叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Grus japonensis</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻译过来就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>日本鹤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/23f6eda19c51467781cef50b44a01d97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早年间有个<strong>德国动物学家</strong>搞研究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备给一些新物种命名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而他搞研究的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好撞上了中国和日本都<strong>闭关</strong>的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他顶多只能从中国广州</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者日本长崎获取点信息资源</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b3250aeab81d4fd98d41005270c53b4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好巧不巧的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹顶鹤冬天<strong>迁徙</strong>去的地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是中国广州</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是日本九州</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而长崎它就在<strong>九州岛</strong>这块</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在日本了解到丹顶鹤的这位动物学家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然而然地把它命名为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——日本鹤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让原本的夺冠热门丹顶鹤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">失去了自己的奖杯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/e78bc77f02304f38826d80fbc68ce9b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只剩最后一名选手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们欢迎——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/42909078c4e54df1a41a0915f5948232.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201106/fe6cec175d074509b3536b0bdddeae43.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201106/9984c834bda24f17a420c5dc80225710.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>朱鹮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光名字就有一股不同的气质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它紧跟时尚潮流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堪称<strong>鸟界变装博主</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">展翅之前平平无奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就头部那块秃头红很显眼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201106/fe59d74fbb2b4ec987980985e9a14367.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但展翅之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宛如人间仙鸟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这羽毛这配色这气质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不愧是<strong>“东方宝石”</strong>本鸟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201106/ae3efb5df9264ad3ad3f4d1741167bb4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和其他两位参赛选手对比</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱鹮也有着牛逼的代表作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《朱鹮飞回来了》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此作荣登小学语文课本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201106/e52633fbf4314c45a0877cbea3ac8614.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于为什么它能获此殊荣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那真是全靠它<strong>非·常·稀·有</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因环境破坏以及肆意捕杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">使得朱鹮陷入灭绝危机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至在1964～1980年间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没人再见到过朱鹮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人一度认为朱鹮已经<strong>灭绝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/0ac1ea08331146ac8b1e094ffb0f381a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到1981年5月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国科学院动物研究所专家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才发现了<strong>七只</strong>朱鹮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让中国成了唯一一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有野生朱鹮的国家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这也次发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是《朱鹮飞回来了》的<strong>故事原型</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d1cc62f53ce4495fb97c23091a96728c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就冲着这个珍稀程度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱鹮拿下国鸟请就位奖杯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎也是势在必得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201106/e552571fdeac4db6a36b38ae5fc278c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是<strong>成也稀有败也稀有</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还外加同样的<strong>debuff</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">名字不过关</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201106/9d4cf9b37dcb46c6ae4159be557738d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当年递上参赛名单时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱鹮虽然已经脱离了灭绝边缘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但仅有200只的数量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人感觉它半只脚还在灭绝坑里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这国鸟选出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二年就灭绝的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实在是有点<strong>尴尬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b1bc329d3fbd442db34e2b71bf129ab0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅如此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱鹮的<strong>拉丁文学名</strong>就更过分了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Nipponia nippon</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Nippon就是日语里的日本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻译过来就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“象征日本的鸟”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“日本冠鹮”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论是哪个都让人无法接受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201106/135ccc58c1dd44b09a1e949aeccee865.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以上三位热门夺冠选手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">均在国鸟请出道大赛中落选</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不禁让人感到可惜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在我们只能期待</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在广袤的中国大地上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有更优秀的鸟类出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向着国鸟的奖杯发起冲击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/685844c71ad24238bd437f1ef7f17e67.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
